---
title: Holiday Spiced Pork Ribs with DIY Choc-Cinnamon Rolls
description: Warm Holiday spiced ribs get a kiss of holiday cheer! A sweet cranberry BBQ dipping sauce, tender-crisp green beans and creamy mash complete this holiday twist! Featuring an after-dinner dessert, make some chocolate cinnamon rolls to enjoy by the fire!
